videos.description: Memphis running back Darrell Henderson gets the hand off and shows off the wheels for the long 62-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Memphis RB takes off for 62-yard TD

videos.description: Memphis running back Darrell Henderson scores from 12 yards out for his second touchdown of the day.
videos.headline: Memphis' Henderson scores 2nd TD of the day

videos.description: UCF running back Greg McCrae sprints through a hole and scores the 14-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF RB scoots through hole for TD

videos.description: Memphis running back Patrick Taylor Jr. takes the direct snap then shows off the speed for a 70-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Memphis RB takes direct snap, breaks free for 70-yard TD

videos.description: UCF's Darriel Mack Jr. loses the football going into the end zone but it's recovered by TE Michael Colubiable for the touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF recovers fumble in end zone for TD

videos.description: UCF quarterback Darriel Mack Jr. throws the perfect lob pass to tight end Jake Hescock for the 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF scores on lob to TE

videos.description: Memphis running back Darrell Henderson has already run for 3 touchdowns, now he throws for one, finding Sean Dykes in the back of the end zone.
videos.headline: Memphis RB throws 4-yard TD

videos.description: UCF wide receiver Otis Anderson catches a long pass and gives the peace sign to a Memphis defender as he scores a 54-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF WR gives peace sign as he scores TD

videos.description: UCF quarterback Darriel Mack Jr. keeps it and scores the 4-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: UCF QB runs it in from 4 yards out

videos.description: UCF's Darriel Mack Jr. powers through a tackler and scores a 2-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Mack's scores 2nd rushing TD gives UCF lead

videos.description: UCF's Darriel Mack Jr. powers his way into the end zone for a 2-yard TD, giving him three scores in the game.
videos.headline: Mack Jr. gets 3rd rushing TD of game

videos.description: Darriel Mack Jr. ties the UCF single-game record with four rushing touchdowns.
videos.headline: Mack Jr. can't be stopped on 4th rushing TD

videos.description: McKenzie Milton's mom celebrates UCF's win by FaceTiming with McKenzie Milton.
videos.headline: Milton's mom FaceTimes McKenzie Milton after UCF win

videos.description: UCF quarterback Darriel Mack Jr. discusses his success in the game today saying this one was for McKenzie Milton.
videos.headline: Mack Jr.: This one's for McKenzie

videos.description: UCF was down by 17 points at halftime then Darriel Mack Jr. ran for four touchdowns in the second half and the Knights come back and beat Memphis 56-41.
